        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[疑问]#为什么肥胖的人更易患糖尿病#】肥胖的人内脏脂肪多，产生的炎症因子会抑制胰岛素分泌，导致血糖升高。但导致糖尿病的因素不只有肥胖，熬夜、不运动、压...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%9B%B4%E6%98%93%E6%82%A3%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%82%A5%E8%83%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%9B%B4%E6%98%93%E6%82%A3%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为什么肥胖的人更易患糖尿病#</span></a>】肥胖的人内脏脂肪多，产生的炎症因子会抑制胰岛素分泌，导致血糖升高。但导致糖尿病的因素不只有肥胖，熬夜、不运动、压力大等不健康的生活方式都有可能使血糖升高，因此瘦人也可能会得糖尿病。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生表示，已经被诊断为糖尿病的年轻人，减少油腻饮食、总热量摄入，增加蔬菜和蛋白质的摄入，减少总热量摄入等，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%96%E8%83%BD%E9%80%86%E8%BD%AC%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%96%E8%83%BD%E9%80%86%E8%BD%AC%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康的生活方式或能逆转糖尿病#</span></a> <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[努力]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/7c/2022_Keepgoing_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6jqLma6" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
